{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "19", "m": "05", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "07", "M": "34", "S": "08"}}, "news": [{"title": "Orissa high court stays suspension on sand quarry lessee", "para": "The Orissa High Court has ruled that statutory authorities cannot usurp powers not expressly conferred by law. The court stayed an interim suspension order on a sand quarry lessee, finding no provision in the Odisha Minor Mineral Concession Rules, 2016, for such immediate action pending adjudication of alleged violations.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/allied-industries/orissa-high-court-blocks-sand-quarry-lessees-suspension/131193831?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-1462183/131193831.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "allied-industries"}, {"title": "Rajasthan: RIICO gets nearly 800 applications for 465 plots", "para": "RIICO received nearly 800 applications for 465 industrial plots valued at Rs 550 crore, primarily for the Kankani Industrial Area in Jodhpur. To boost occupancy in underutilised zones, RIICO revised its policy, offering plots at 60% of the prevailing rate. This initiative saw a significant rise in applications for these areas.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/riico-surges-with-800-applications-for-465-industrial-plots-in-rajasthan/131189801?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-189632/131189801.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "NeoLiv acquires 76 acres land in Maharashtra's Khopoli for plotted development, villa project", "para": "NeoLiv has acquired a 76-acre land parcel in Khopoli near Mumbai. This marks their third plotted development in the Panvel-Khopoli belt. The company plans a mixed-use community with villas, plots, and retail. The project has an estimated Gross Development Value of Rs 800 crore. This acquisition is a significant milestone for NeoLiv's expansion in a sought-after micro-market.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/neoliv-expands-its-footprint-with-76-acre-land-acquisition-in-khopoli-for-luxury-villas-and-residential-development/131189708?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-235538/131189708.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}]}